   <section id="content">
    <div class="single post-1613 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-cool-vws category-vw-blog tag-camper tag-pop-top tag-vw-bus" id="post-1613">
     <h1 class="single-post-title">
      The Coolest Poptop VW Camper Buses Youve Ever Seen
     </h1>
     <div class="single-post-meta">
      by Jason Lancaster on February 3, 2015
     </div>
     <div class="entry single clear">
      <p>
       The VW Bus is one of the coolest vehicles ever made. Chock full of versatility and novelty, the Bus has a cult following. Here are some of the coolest pop top VW camper Buses around.
      </p>
      <p>
       <span id="more-1613">
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1974-westfalia.jpg">
        <img alt="1974 Westfalia Bus" class=" size-full wp-image-1614 aligncenter" height="457" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1974-westfalia.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1974-westfalia2.jpg">
        <img alt="1974 Westfalia Interior" class=" size-full wp-image-1618 aligncenter" height="457" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1974-westfalia2.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.sunsetclassics.com/1974-vw-bus-pop-top/" target="_blank">
        1974 Westfalia Bus
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       This pop top bus has a cool and soft blue interior, mood lighting, and a spacious living area in the main cabin. Theres also a RV hookup that allows occupants to plug in appliances just as if they were home.
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1969-west-pop-top.jpg">
        <img alt="1969 West Pop Top" class=" size-full wp-image-1615 aligncenter" height="522" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1969-west-pop-top.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.oldbug.com/lindatanwesty.htm" target="_blank">
        1969 West Pop Top
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       A very clean Bus, this awesome VW was restored and finished off with an extremely glossy paint job. This tent on wheels features a comfortable lounge space and storage galore!
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1966-skylit-westy.jpg">
        <img alt="1966 Skylit Westy" class=" size-full wp-image-1616 aligncenter" height="479" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1966-skylit-westy.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.curbsideclassic.com/blog/car-show-classics-the-2012-bi-state-vw-club-show-hope-you-like-beetles-and-buses/" target="_blank">
        1966 Skylit Westy
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       This is especially cool for campers as this bus has a skylight built into the pop top! With this cool Bus, you can sleep under the stars without bugs flying up your nose while you sleep.
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1967-westy-camper-bus.jpg">
        <img alt="1967 Westy Camper Bus" class=" size-full wp-image-1617 aligncenter" height="494" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1967-westy-camper-bus.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.waveweapons.com/vwbuses/" target="_blank">
        1967 Westy Camper Bus
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       What an awesome classic bus with louvered windows and a smaller pop-top than some of the others. This perfectly restored Bus is sure to make road trips and camping something else!
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1970-double-tent-bus.jpg">
        <img alt="1970 Double Tent Bus" class=" size-full wp-image-1619 aligncenter" height="480" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1970-double-tent-bus.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.oldbug.com/jacobs70.htm" target="_blank">
        1970 Double Tent Bus
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       This bus has two tents for the ultimate camping experience with a Bus. One pops up from the top, and one sets up beside the Bus for lounging on the camp grounds.
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan.jpg">
        <img alt="1971 Westfalia VW Campervan" class=" size-full wp-image-1620 aligncenter" height="480" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan2.jpg">
        <img alt="1971 Westfalia VW Campervan Interior" class=" size-full wp-image-1621 aligncenter" height="480" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan2.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan3.jpg">
        <img alt="1971 Westfalia VW Campervan Engine" class=" size-full wp-image-1622 aligncenter" height="480" src="http://www.vwpartsvortex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1971-westfalia-vw-campervan3.jpg" width="640"/>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
